My Zootopia_with_API Project
A Python project that fetches animal data from the [API Ninjas Animal API](https://api-ninjas.com/api/animals)
and generates a dynamic HTML website using that data.
This repository is  a part of my Zootopia_with_API project in codio.

Features

- Fetches real animal info via an API
- Renders an HTML page with animal cards
- Uses a `.env` file to securely store API keys
- Modular structure for clean code

Installation
To install this project, simply clone the repository and install the dependencies in requirements.txt using pip

Usage
To use this project, run the following command - animals_web_generator.py.

